<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: A Wizards Poin of View.</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Tilran">Tilran</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 12:28 p.m. 28/5/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: A Wizards Poin of View.<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2102" TARGET=_self>A Wizards Poin of View.</A> (Jim)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>

<BR>First of all...im a wizard level 16, i do not agree with the views downing wizards one bit. You say root is so
<BR>strong and paralyzes everything...well let me tell you something...its not...when it DOES work it lasts for about
<BR>5 seconds...only rarely does it acctully work good. As for Gate, this spell does NOTHING in PvP unless the
<BR>player is rooted. Gate takes so damn long to cast that its only purpose is to get from one place to another. i
<BR>cant remember the guys name few posts ago who said gate was quicker then 1 round of combat but hes
<BR>more wacko then darknyss (who thinks wizards get pets). Gate takes around 3 combat rounds to cast....unless
<BR>the person you are fighting is so helpless they cant even HIT you...you are not gating...wizards dont get any type
<BR>of speed spell like SoW so a warrior quickly runs them down. Wizards ARE NOT overpowered what so ever and
<BR>DO take a long time to level. They have VERY low armor class and even lower hit points. You people downing
<BR>Wizards try and play one, see what happens. Now....for the eq loss you warriors say you lose when wizards kill
<BR>you. First of all when yer higher a wizard has a hard time killing you. Second we are NOT naked while attacking.
<BR>Sure the newbies might be, but not the decent level wizards. I personnaly have rings/earrings and bracelets
<BR>that are worth around 30 plat due to magic abilitys on them such as +10mana +10hp etc etc..
<BR>You warriors have it so easy compared to us. If you wanna down a magic class down one with a pet. THEY
<BR>are the ones who are overpowered (EX: Necromancers). Wizards and Clerics are the only classes i believe
<BR>have to acctully try in this game.
<P>Very Ticked Off Wizard
<BR>Tilran (Dark Brigade)
<BR>
